      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "text": "Subtracting with 10-Complement (Borrowing)"
      },
      {
        "type": "callout",
        "style": "info",
        "text": "When subtracting more than available: SUBTRACT 1 from tens column, ADD the complement to ones."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Example: 13 - 8"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "items": [
          "Set 13 (1 in tens, 3 in ones)",
          "Subtract 8 from ones... only 3 there! Not enough.",
          "Complement of 8 is 2",
          "Subtract 1 from tens, add 2 to ones: 3 + 2 = 5",
          "Result: 5 ✓"
        ]
      },
      {
