      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "text": "Combining 5 and 10 Complements"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Some problems need BOTH techniques. Example: 8 + 6"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "items": [
          "8 + 6 = 14",
          "First handle the carry (10-complement): add 10, subtract 4",
          "8 - 4 needs the 5-complement: subtract 5, add 1",
          "Final: 8 - 4 = 4, plus 1 ten = 14 ✓"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "callout",
        "style": "tip",
        "text": "This combined technique sounds complex, but with practice it becomes a single fluid motion. The brain automates the steps."
      }
